          <h2>2. Step 2: Master Keyword Research with Semrush <i class="fas fa-keyboard icon-inline"></i></h2>
          <p>Keyword research is the backbone of any successful SEO strategy, and Semrush provides an unparalleled suite of tools to help you find the most profitable keywords for your business. With over 24 billion keywords in its database, Semrush enables you to uncover hidden gems, analyze SERP features, and build a data-backed content plan that drives both traffic and conversions.</p>
